# Turbo Workspace Commands

Run commands from the repository root unless a package-local command is explicitly needed.

Common commands:

```bash
pnpm dev
pnpm build
pnpm lint
pnpm db:generate
pnpm db:push
```

Use filters for focused work:

```bash
pnpm turbo run dev --filter=@meicontrol/web
pnpm turbo run dev --filter=@meicontrol/api
pnpm turbo run build --filter=@meicontrol/web
pnpm turbo run lint --filter=@meicontrol/api
pnpm --filter @meicontrol/api test
pnpm --filter @meicontrol/database db:migrate
```

`dev` is persistent and uncached. `build` caches `.next/**` and `dist/**`. Prisma generation and push tasks are uncached.
